\b Converting existing Keyrings\
\

\b0 If you do not intend to use your keyring with GnuPG 1.x or 2.0.x in the future, we recommend that you convert your keyring to the new GnuPG 2.1 format. This will speed up any keyring operations. However, the drawback is that you keyring is not compatible to GnuPG versions before 2.1.\
\
