1. Open a Terminal window \
2. Execute: 
\f2 sha1sum Downloads/GnuPG-2.1.0.dmg\

\f1 3. Click on the (i) button at the right side of the download bar on the download page. \
4. Compare the checksum you got in the Terminal with the SHA1 sum on the web page.\
